DESCRIPTION:Twice a month in the Guild Room\, usually the first and third Wednesday at noon. \nSages is a group of older members and friends that meet twice a month for a brown bag lunch and informal discussion of questions and issues that are relevant in that stage of their lives. The purpose of the group is to build community and support by providing a forum for discussion and gathering as a community.
