SUMMARY:From Hadoop to BigQuery: A Practical\, Zero-Downtime Migration Pla
 ybook​
DESCRIPTION:Cloud Data Driven\nLegacy Hadoop-based data lakes struggle wit
 h scalability\, cost\, and operational complexity. In this session\, I’l
 l walk through a real-world cloud data migration strategy for moving large
 -scale enterprise data lakes from Hadoop to Google BigQuery without downti
 me.\n\nThe talk covers:\n\\- Designing parallel pipelines to ensure busine
 ss continuity\\.\n\\- Handling schema evolution and data validation at sca
 le\\.\n\\- Ensuring data quality and accuracy across millions of records\\
 .\n\\- Optimizing performance and cost in a cloud\\-native analytics stack
 \\.\n\nThis session is grounded in hands-on enterprise experience supporti
 ng revenue analytics\, reporting\, and AI-driven use cases in production e
 nvironments.\n\nLearning Objective\nBy the end of this session\, attendees
  will be able to:\n\\- Design a zero\\-downtime data lake migration strate
 gy\n\\- Implement validation frameworks to ensure data accuracy post\\-mig
 ration\n\\- Understand common pitfalls when modernizing Hadoop\\-based sys
 tems\n\\- Apply cloud\\-native best practices for scalable analytics
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/cloud-data-driven/events/313269125/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260208T201818Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260208T201818Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
