SUMMARY:Loopwell x Merrill Lynch: Financial Well-Being — Navigating Life’s Transitions
DESCRIPTION:Life’s transitions — whether retirement\, divorce\, empty nesting\, career shifts\, or loss — can feel overwhelming\, especially when financial decisions feel heavy and uncertain. Join us for a thoughtful\, human-centered conversation exploring financial wellbeing as a deeply personal part of life and identity. This isn’t a lecture or sales pitch — it’s a space for honest dialogue\, reflection\, connection\, and grounding as you navigate meaningful life chapters. \nShare this:\n				Share on Facebook (Opens in new window)\n				Facebook\n			\n				Share on Bluesky (Opens in new window)\n				Bluesky\n			\n				Share on LinkedIn (Opens in new window)\n				LinkedIn\n			\n				Share on Threads (Opens in new window)\n				Threads\n			\n				Share on Nextdoor (Opens in new window)\n				Nextdoor\n			\n				Share on WhatsApp (Opens in new window)\n				WhatsApp\n			\n				Email a link to a friend (Opens in new window)\n				Email
