LAST-MODIFIED:20260316T233414Z
UID:10138262-1773964800-1776643199@montclairlocal.news
SUMMARY:The Museum Makes Art: MAM’s Creative Community
DESCRIPTION:This exhibition celebrates the creativity of the Montclair Art Museum community by showcasing artwork by our staff\, docents\, art educators\, Board members\, and members of MAM’s African American Cultural Committee (AACC). \nMAM’s mission statement reads\, “Through art\, we create experiences that inspire\, challenge\, and foster community to shape our shared future.” While this statement speaks to the purpose and values that we strive to share with all of our visitors\, it also reflects the collective culture cultivated by the people working within the museum offices\, art studios\, galleries\, and behind the scenes. Featuring 53 artists\, the work on view is as multifaceted as the Museum and includes a wide range of artistic mediums and techniques. Each piece expresses unique ideas and perspectives that we hope will spark conversation and creativity. \nShare this:\n				Share on Facebook (Opens in new window)\n				Facebook\n			\n				Share on Bluesky (Opens in new window)\n				Bluesky\n			\n				Share on LinkedIn (Opens in new window)\n				LinkedIn\n			\n				Share on Threads (Opens in new window)\n				Threads\n			\n				Share on Nextdoor (Opens in new window)\n				Nextdoor\n			\n				Share on WhatsApp (Opens in new window)\n				WhatsApp\n			\n				Email a link to a friend (Opens in new window)\n				Email
URL:https://montclairlocal.news/event/the-museum-makes-art-mams-creative-community/
LOCATION:Montclair Art Museum\, 3 South Mountain Ave\, Montclair\, NJ\, 07042\, United States
CATEGORIES:Art & Culture
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://montclairlocal.news/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Aries-by-Angela-Beekers-Uberi.jpg
GEO:40.8185787;-74.2242523
X-APPLE-STRUCTURED-LOCATION;VALUE=URI;X-ADDRESS=Montclair Art Museum 3 South Mountain Ave Montclair NJ 07042 United States;X-APPLE-RADIUS=500;X-TITLE=3 South Mountain Ave:geo:-74.2242523,40.8185787
END:VEVENT
