X-SOURCE-ID:meetup_north_jersey_bowling_soccer_volleyball
X-SOURCE:Meetup: NJ Bowling, Volleyball, Tennis & More
UID:event_313711394@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260318T024947Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260320T190000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260320T210000
SUMMARY:Billiards
DESCRIPTION:North Jersey Bowling\, Volleyball\, Tennis And More (BVT)\n***
 Meeting Point:***\nOutside of the building\; After 5-10 minutes: You can m
 eet us upstairs at the pool tables. *\\*\\*Please look for the group as th
 e staff do not keep up with the group\\*\\***\n*** Price:\nThe price is $6
 .50 per hour per person if you have 4 players at your table. However\, the
  final price is based on the total amount of minutes played. At the end of
  the hour\, the table amount will be split per person. Each table should h
 ave a table leader\, **this person will collect the money of players at th
 eir table and will pay for the table on one card.** 3-4 table leaders will
  be needed\, **volunteering for this is encouraged**\n\n***Bringing cash i
 s highly encouraged to pay your portion to your table leader***\n\n*Parkin
 g*: street parking is available however it may be hard to find close to th
 e venue. There are side streets before the town proper\, but a good option
  is the nearby ANT bookstore which has a lot which should be okay to use.\
 n\n***This location has food & drinks available for purchase.***\n\n*** Ex
 pectations**:\nPool cues are available at the location\, expect mid to low
  lighting. If you come after 7:15pm\, look for the Meetup group upstairs.\
 n** *What if I'm a beginner or only want to play with people at a similar 
 level?**\nTables will be divided between beginners\, intermediate players\
 , and advanced. However\, this depends on how many types of players come\,
  so it will be divided as best as possibly available. If you would like ga
 me rules\, please speak with Marc.** Marc is also available to answer ques
 tions including how to hold the cue\, stances\, etc.**\n*** Is anyone at C
 lifton Billiards after 9pm?\nAfter 9pm\, most go home or go to a local bar
 . If you'd like to hang out after\, definitely speak with members to see i
 f they want to do something after.\n*** Can I switch tables?**\n*Yes\, but
  it does make it easier if you stay at your table. If you switch tables\, 
 pay the amount of time you were at that table. Example\, if you were at ab
 le A for an hour\, pay the hour to the table A leader. If you go table B f
 or two hours\, pay your two hours to the table B leader. At the end\, the 
 table leader is taking the payments for the total amount of time at that t
 able.*\n*** How do I get balls for the table and how many people do I tell
  staff that I have?*\n*One person per table gives their ID to the staff in
  order to check out balls. Again\, the price for 4 people is about $6.50. 
 If you have more or less\, it slightly changes. So it just depends on how 
 many people are at your table. It may be better to mention that you have m
 ore people esp if you are starting with 4 or 5 people.*\n*** I feel like p
 eople aren't trying to be my friend.*\n*Please remember that different peo
 ple have different goals. Some may come to just play billiards\, others ma
 y be there to meet new people or do something social\, and some may be the
 re to make long term friends. Find people that match your goals or be ok w
 ith others that may not.
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/north-jersey-bowling-soccer-volleybal
 l/events/313711394/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260309T134945Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260309T134945Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
