SUMMARY:Rinc go deo! The DeNogla Academy of Irish Dance
DESCRIPTION:Rinc go deo (dance forever)! Students from the DeNogla Academy 
 of Irish Dance will keep the St. Patrick’s Day celebrations going with a 
 performance of riveting Irish Dance! The DeNogla Academy of Irish Dance has 
 been home to regional\, national\, and world champion Irish dancers since 
 1993. No registration required.\n\n
