DESCRIPTION:Join us for a night written in the stars!\nTadhana\, the Filip
 ino word for destiny and fate\, is the unseen force that guides our stori
 es\, even when we don’t realize it. MUFASA invites you to step into that 
 magic at our annual cultural ball inspired by precolonial Filipino mythol
 ogy.\nCome dressed as a deity\, monster\, or myth that speaks to you. Thi
 s is a night for self-expression\, creativity\, and honoring our heritage
  while choosing how we show up in the present.\nWhile we celebrate Filipi
 no culture at the heart of Tadhana\, all cultures\, identities\, and back
 grounds are wholeheartedly welcome. Whether you’re channeling an ancestor
 \, a legend\, or your own destiny\, there is space for you at Tadhana.\n\
 nHosted by: Montclair Unified Filipino American Student Association\n\nAd
 ditional Information can be found at: https://montclair.campuslabs.com/en
 gage/event/12309796
DTEND:20260322T013000Z
DTSTAMP:20260318T024951Z
DTSTART:20260321T220000Z
