UID:TU2042067998
RECURRENCE-ID;TZID=America/New_York:20260322T130000
SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:Events
CLASS:PUBLIC
CREATED:20260212T183231Z
DESCRIPTION:Join Rabbi Julie and President Aaron Delaney in a series of di
 scussions around the Interfaith Community.\n\nRabbi Julie will be hosting 
 a series of three community meetings in February and March\, where she wil
 l present background information about interfaith families\, including abo
 ut the demographics of our community and the policies of the Conservative 
 Movement on this issue. Participants in these meetings will be invited to 
 give input and engage in dialogue with the Rabbi\, Aaron Delaney\, and wit
 h other members of the community as we share perspectives around this topi
 c.\n\nBabysitting will be available at the Sunday sessions upon request (e
 mail Aviva Arad aarad@shomrei.org).\n\nThe dates of the Community Meetings
  are as follows:\n\nSunday\, February 22\, 10:00 – 11:30am\n\nTuesday\, 
 March 3\, 8:00 – 9:30pm\, Zoom Only (https://shomrei.org/z\\_rabbijulie:
  https://shomrei.org/z_rabbijulie)\n\nSunday\, March 22\, 1:00 – 2:30pm 
 at the social hall\n\nPlease remember to bring your fob to access the buil
 ding.\n\n
LAST-MODIFIED:20260313T043409Z
TRANSP:OPAQUE
URL;VALUE=URI:https://teamup.com/kstx8swyw669kakgqa/events/2042067998
