SUMMARY:Period Party: A Menstruation Celebration (Ages 7-14)
DESCRIPTION:A thoughtful laidback celebration to add joy to and reduce the 
 stigma when it comes to menstruation. Join us for an afternoon of 
 encouragement\, delicious sweet treats\, open dialogue\, and of course take 
 home gifts. This supportive gathering is for the girls in their tweens\, 
 and their caregivers to feel empowered and connected to a community of 
 women. Registration encouraged for a headcount but not required\n\n
LOCATION:Montclair Main - Classroom\, Montclair Main - Teen Room
ORGANIZER;CN="Montclair Library":MAILTO:events@montclairlibrary.org
