  the 30-hour Ethics and Agency Broker course as part of New Jersey?s requi
 red 150-hour Broker pre-licensing curriculum. This instructor-led program 
 supports broker candidates by strengthening ethical judgment\, agency rela
 tionships\, and supervisory responsibilities. The full 150-hour Broker pre
 -licensing requirement includes: 30 Hours – Ethics & Agency 30 Hours –
