SUMMARY:Awakening Awareness: Embracing This Moment
DESCRIPTION:The Mindful Stream\nFeel free to join as we get still and prac
 tise presence within this moment. We will discuss and observe the obstacle
 s that\, seemingly\, block us from being present and bring awareness to ou
 r unconsciousness in a safe\, inclusive and affirming way.\n\nSessions are
  suitable for newcomers\, those experienced in Tolle's teaching and anyone
  wishing to remain completely anonymous.\n\nSee you there!\n\nPlease be aw
 are that sessions will close if no members have joined after 10 minutes.\n
 \nEmrys has been passionate about mindfulness since 2010 and since 2021 he
  has been organising free\, weekly online meditation groups. For more info
 rmation on his free Work of Byron Katie online mediation group\, visit [th
 is Meetup Group link](https://www.meetup.com/thework-runsfree/).
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/themindfulstream/events/313644285/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260305T032714Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260305T032714Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
