SUMMARY:Stretch\, Resistance & Light Cardio
DESCRIPTION:This is a paid Adult School class. Click here to register on 
 the Adult School website.\n\nAccording to medical professionals\, it is 
 important to keep the body flexible & the bones strong. The synovial fluid 
 in our joints is extremely important for good movement. Strong muscles act 
 like shock absorbers to protect our bones. With resistance exercises\, the 
 bones and muscles will stay or become stronger. Light hand & leg weights 
 optional.
LOCATION:Montclair - First Lutheran Church\, Montclair Public Library
ORGANIZER;CN="Montclair Adult School":MAILTO:adultschool@montclairlibrary.org
CATEGORIES:Adult School, Fitness
UID:LibCal-10306-15993404
URL:https://bccls.libcal.com/event/15993404
END:VEVENT
