SUMMARY:Mediterranean Cooking Demo & Tasting NEW
DESCRIPTION:Registration closes on March 18. This is a paid Adult School 
 class. Click here to register.\n\nFor years\, the Mediterranean diet has 
 been touted for its many health benefits. But how do you incorporate those 
 principles into your daily cooking? Join olive oil sommelier and Firenze 
 Olive Oil owner Donna Liotto-Scocozza as she demonstrates the fine points 
 of making a Mediterranean meal that’s just right for the new spring 
 season.\n\nYou'll get to sample a mini portion of all these delicacies at 
 the end of class:\n\n\n	Welcome spring surprise bruschetta\n	Mixed salad 
 with sunny lemon-basil-honey vinaigrette\n	Asparagus & early spring pea 
 risotto\n	Vanilla gelato topped with a choice of three flavor-infused 
 extra-virgin olive oils\n
LOCATION:Montclair Main - Auditorium\, Montclair Public Library
ORGANIZER;CN="Montclair Adult School":MAILTO:adultschool@montclairlibrary.org
