SUMMARY:Film Club - In-Person
DESCRIPTION:This is a paid Adult School class. Click here to 
 register.\n\nDo you love to go to the movies and discuss them? See selected 
 movies which are mostly art/indie and Oscar-nominated films at the 
 Clairidge Theater in Montclair. Then join classmates to talk about themes\, 
 plot\, characters\, acting\, directing\, cinematography\, costumes\, 
 score\, trailers and viewer’s expectations. Feb. 11\, 25\, Mar. 11\, 25\, 
 May 6\, 20\, and June 3\, 17 .take place at Congregation Shomrei Emunah. 
 Apr. 8 and 22 which take place at the First Lutheran Church.
