DESCRIPTION:Shape The Future Of Work \nOrganizations are seeking experts w
 ho can apply data-driven strategies to improve performance\, drive engage
 ment\, and create thriving work environments. With Montclair's Industrial
 /Organizational Psychology (PhD)\, you’ll gain the advanced skills to sha
 pe the future of work and position yourself for top career opportunities.
 Registration is LIVE for our virtual information session March 26 at 6:00
  PM (EST). Explore how our faculty conduct research that influences HR\, 
 talent management\, and organizational development. \n\nHosted by: The Of
 fice of Graduate Admissions\n\nOnline Location: https://graduate.montclai
 r.edu/register/?id=24b35c61-0a67-4be6-b360-38d6baef5d09\n\nAdditional Inf
 ormation can be found at: https://montclair.campuslabs.com/engage/event/1
