BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Campuslabs Montclair": "https://montclair.campuslabs.com/engage/event/12330880"}
X-SOURCE-ID:campuslabs_montclair
X-SOURCE:Montclair State University
CATEGORIES:Arts
DESCRIPTION:The Reawakening of the Gods\nA Public Reading of a New Musical
 \nFriday\, March 27\, 2026 at 8:00 PMLeshowitz Recital HallJohn J. Cali S
 chool of MusicMontclair State University\nThe John J. Cali School of Musi
 c\, in collaboration with the Inserra Chair in Italian and Italian Americ
 an Studies and the Musical Theatre Program\, presents a public reading of
  The Reawakening of the Gods\, a new musical written and directed by Marc
 o Savatteri and produced in partnership with Savatteri Produzioni.\nThis 
 staged reading will be interpreted by students from the Cali School’s Mus
 ical Theatre Program (CART)\, with assistance from Toti Maria Geraci and 
 accompaniment by David Fraley. The event also features brief talks by Ter
 esa Fiore\, an English translation by Brianna Coppolino\, and reflections
  on the Savatteri internship experience by Mia Grizzuti.\nBlending classi
 cal themes with contemporary musical storytelling\, The Reawakening of th
 e Gods offers audiences an opportunity to experience the development of n
 ew work while engaging with an international creative collaboration. This
  special event highlights the Cali School’s commitment to interdisciplina
 ry performance\, global artistic exchange\, and student-centered creative
  practice.\nAdmission: Free and open to the publicMore information: tinyu
 rl.com/ReadingReawakening\n\nHosted by: The College of the Arts\n\nAdditi
 onal Information can be found at: https://montclair.campuslabs.com/engage
 /event/12330880
DTEND:20260328T013000Z
DTSTAMP:20260318T024951Z
DTSTART:20260328T000000Z
GEO:40.859750;-74.199750
LOCATION:Leshowitz Recital Hall
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:CALI SCHOOL OF MUSIC | The Reawakening of the Gods - Musical Readi
 ng
