SUMMARY:Underground Church Worship Service\,10:30am on the Labyrinth in th
 e Sanctuary
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260328T103000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260328T120000
DTSTAMP:20260318T024952Z
UID:65u2v4m892p76jtahmvgna6mvb@google.com__20260328
SEQUENCE:2
CREATED:20251001T145422Z
DESCRIPTION:<span></span><span>Underground Church (usually every 3rd Satu
 rday) is a unique and dynamic gathering that meets monthly\, and combines 
 the intimacy of Jesus' early community with creative and inventive worship
  experiences.  In the warmth and safety of community we explore the scrip
 tures\, live out the questions through discussion\,  and share innovative
  rituals that bring us closer to each other and to our still-speaking God.
  Together we create the unity of spirit that helps us find God's presence 
 in the messy and beautiful experience of living today.  All are welcome.<
 /span>
LAST-MODIFIED:20260310T152948Z
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:OPAQUE
