DESCRIPTION:Stars\, stripes\, and some serious smarts! ????? Join us for P
 atriotic Trivia\, a fast-paced\, fun-filled event where you can test your
  knowledge of U.S. history\, government\, iconic moments\, and all things
  red\, white\, and blue!\nWhether you’re a history buff or just in it for
  the fun\, this is your chance to show off what you know\, learn somethin
 g new\, and enjoy some friendly competition with fellow students\, facult
 y\, and staff.\nFrom the Constitution to pop culture\, the questions will
  keep you guessing—and prizes are up for grabs! Come solo or bring a team
 \, and get ready for an exciting celebration of civic knowledge and natio
 nal pride.\nThink you’ve got what it takes? Let’s find out—one trivia que
 stion at a time! Stop by\, enjoy some pizza and you might even win some r
 eally cool prizes\n\nHosted by: Civic & Voter Engagement\, Campus Activit
 ies at Bloomfield\n\nAdditional Information can be found at: https://mont
 clair.campuslabs.com/engage/event/12266498
