DESCRIPTION:<span>The word "tenebrae" comes from the Latin word meaning"sh
 adows."  On this night we confront the shadow side of our faith.  Throug
 h contemplative sacred music\, scripture story\, reflection and  hymns w
 e will share the story of Jesus' trial\, crucifixion and death.  As th
 e light grows dimmer we are invited to stand at the foot of the cross and 
 share this powerful experience.  </span><b><i><span>You are asked to wea
 r black clothing to this service.</span></i></b><b><i> </i></b><span><br><
 br></span>
