 le in the pool. Learn how to use proper breath control\, float\, and swim
  with a kickboard. \nSkills Focus:\n\nBeing comfortable in the water\nLea
 rning how to float on your back and front\nLearning how to kick off the w
 all with a kickboard\nIntroducing proper breath control in the water\nLea
 rning how to tread water\nLearn alternate kicks (Froggy Kick)\nBeing comf
 ortable in the deep end \nIntroducing arms to your strokes\n\nHow do I Si
 gn-up?\n\nRegistration is not required\nFREE with a valid Montclair State
  ID\n\nWhen and Where?\n\nTuesday: 5-6PM\nStudent Recreation Center - Poo
 l \n\n\nHosted by: Campus Recreation\n\nAdditional Information can be fou
 nd at: https://montclair.campuslabs.com/engage/event/11933676
