X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Campuslabs Montclair": "https://montclair.campuslabs.com/engage/event/12267448"}
X-SOURCE-ID:campuslabs_montclair
X-SOURCE:Montclair State University
CATEGORIES:Athletics
DESCRIPTION:Get ready for a scenic spin through history as we ride the leg
 endary Old Croton Aqueduct! This unforgettable bike trip takes you along 
 one of New York’s most beautiful and peaceful trails\, where tree-lined p
 aths\, and charming river views\, create the perfect backdrop for a day o
 utdoors. As we cruise along the trail you’ll enjoy plenty of photo-worthy
  stops along the way. Expect a relaxed pace with time to explore\, snack\
 , and soak in the scenery. Whether you're in it for the fresh air\, the h
 istory\, or just a joyful ride with great company\, this Croton Aqueduct 
 adventure is a perfect blend of nature\, culture\, and fun on two wheels!
  \nHow do I sign-up?\n\nRegister online through Fusion\, in the Student R
 ecreation Center's main office\, or over the phone (973-655-3340).\nCost 
 for Students - $10 | Faculty/Staff - $20\n\nWhen and Where?\n\nSunday\, A
 pril 12\, 2026\n10:00 am - 5:00 pm\nCroton Aqueduct\, NJ - Begins and end
 s at Student Recreation Center\n\nWhat to bring:\n\nMoney for spending\, 
 lunch\, water\, comfortable shoes\, sunscreen.\n\nPotential Hazards: Haza
 rdous weather\, poisonous plants/allergies\, insect bites\, unpredictable
  weather changes\, sunburn/heat exhaustion\, dehydration\, and injuries\,
  including sprains/strains\, abrasions\, lacerations and fractures.\n \n\
 nHosted by: Campus Recreation\n\nAdditional Information can be found at: 
 https://montclair.campuslabs.com/engage/event/12267448
DTEND:20260412T210000Z
DTSTAMP:20260318T024951Z
DTSTART:20260412T140000Z
LOCATION:Meet at Student Recreation Center
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Croton Aqueduct Bike Trip
UID:https://montclair.campuslabs.com/engage/event/12267448
URL:https://montclair.campuslabs.com/engage/event/12267448
