SUMMARY:Shomrei Gives Back - Mitzvah Day
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260419T093000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260419T123000
DTSTAMP:20260313T210315Z
UID:TU1892966145
RECURRENCE-ID;TZID=America/New_York:20260419T093000
SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:Events
CLASS:PUBLIC
CREATED:20250605T135433Z
DESCRIPTION:**2nd Annual Mitzvah Day**  \n  \nGather as a community in ser
 vice to perform mitzvot for our local social action partners\, Israel\, an
 d Shomrei itself. All ages welcome! There is a Mitzvah for everyone\, incl
 uding kids! Babysitting available. Breakfast nosh provided.  \n  \nOpen to
  Shomrei Community &amp\; Friends.  \n  \n**Participate in any or all acti
 vities:**   \n  \n  \n**DONATE SUPPLIES** Donate items needed to make our 
 Mitzvot a reality. Visit our online wish list to make a purchase. Make sur
 e items are delivered to Shomrei **by April 8.** Drop-offs at Shomrei are 
 welcome. Or\, fund the supplies with a monetary donation. You don't have t
 o donate items to participate (but it helps!)  \n**online wish list: https
 ://shomrei.org/wishlist**  \n**alternative monetary donation:** **https://
 shomrei.org/supplies**  \n **VOLUNTEER YOUR TIME**  \nChoose your task whe
 n you arrive\, among:  \n- Assemble Senior grocery bags for Toni's Kitchen
 \n- Sort donated spring &amp\; summer clothes for Human Needs Food Pantry\
 n- Assemble "Welcome to Your New Home" kits for Family Promise\n- Make san
 dwiches for MESH\n- Garden outdoors at Shomrei\n- Make friendship bracelet
 s for a school in Israel (kid-specific)\n- Color pictures/write letters fo
 r seniors (kid-specific)\n- Write thank you cards for pet adoptions for th
 e Montclair Animal Shelter (kid-specific)\n\n  \n**register here: https://
 shomrei.org/mitzvah  \n  \n**PARTICIPATE IN A DRIVE**  \nBring breakfast c
 ereals and/or adult and children’s summer clothing for Human Needs Food 
 Pantry to Shomrei (Drop off at Shomrei or bring with you on Mitzvah day.) 
  \n  \n**Questions?** Contact Melissa Mehl\,   \nOperations Manager  \nmme
 hl@shomrei.org  \n(973) 746-5031\,[](http://voice.google.com/calls?a=nc\,%
 2B19737465031) x101\n\n
LAST-MODIFIED:20260312T151107Z
TRANSP:OPAQUE
URL;VALUE=URI:https://teamup.com/kstx8swyw669kakgqa/events/1892966145
X-SOURCE:Congregation Shomrei Emunah
X-SOURCE-URL:https://shomrei.org/calendar/
END:VEVENT
