DESCRIPTION:WordPress Montclair Meetup\nCome to network\, chat\, talk shop
 \, or just hang out with like-minded WordPress folks. Alcoholic\\* and non
 -alcoholic beverages\, along with a variety of food options will be availa
 ble to purchase. Hope to see you there!\n\nWe will be meeting at Just Jake
 's in the backroom area.\n\n\\*Please be safe and no drinking to excess.\n
 \n\\-\\-\\-\nJoin the **JerseyPress Slack** group to chat with others in o
 ur community and get help: [https://jerseypress.org/slack/](https://jersey
 press.org/slack/)
